  "title": "Retain Cart",
  "content": "\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"hiq-page-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"hiq-t-wrap\">\r\n\t\t\r\n  \t  <div class=\"hiq-t \">\r\n\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"breadcrumbs\"><li><a class=\"breadcrumb-links\" hqid=\"1788908\"  href=\"/home\">Home</a></li> <li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"3500940\" href=\"/omni\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Manhattan Active® Omni</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"3426481\" href=\"/store-3\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Store</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"2158412\" href=\"/process-configuration-guides-3\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Process & Configuration Guides</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"2158737\" href=\"/point-of-sale\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Point of Sale</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"3433322\" href=\"/pos-iris-guides\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">POS Guides</a></li><li> <span>››</span>Retain Cart</li></ul>  \t\r\n\t\t<h2><a name=\"retain-cart\" id=\"retain-cart\"></a>Retain Cart</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"info\"><ul><li><a href=\"/retain-cart$retain-cart\">Retain Cart</a><ul><li><a href=\"/retain-cart$behavior\">Behavior</a></li><li><a href=\"/retain-cart$enablement\">Enablement</a></li><li><a href=\"/retain-cart$use-cases\">Use Cases</a></li></ul></li></ul></div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When a user navigates away from POS, the system preserves the current cart state, ensuring that all relevant details remain available when the user returns. This functionality was created to&nbsp;prevent&nbsp;the loss of cart progress due to navigation actions. The retained cart state includes:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n\t<li>Applied discounts</li>\r\n\t<li>Attached customers</li>\r\n\t<li>Item quantities</li>\r\n\t<li>Selected item(s)</li>\r\n\t<li>Ship to address item(s)</li>\r\n\t<li>Store pickup&nbsp;item(s)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Once user presses&nbsp;checkout and invoice is created, retained cart feature will no longer be available.&nbsp;Once an order is canceled, it cannot be resumed when the user navigates back to the cart page. The system will treat canceled orders as final, requiring the user to initiate a new order if they wish to purchase items again.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"tip\">Note: Retain cart is only activated when items are added to cart.</div>\r\n\r\n<h3><a name=\"behavior\" id=\"behavior\"></a>Behavior</h3>\r\n\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n\t<li value=\"1\">Cart Persistence\r\n\t<ul type=\"circle\">\r\n\t\t<li>Users can freely navigate away from the cart page without losing their selected items and cart details.</li>\r\n\t\t<li>Upon returning, the cart will be restored with all the items that were scanned before ( Cart Mode)</li>\r\n\t\t<li><a href=\"https://omni.helpdocsonline.com/poscartccnfiguration-2-2$retain-cart-allowed-duration\">Configurable timer</a> to set amount of time for item(s) to be retained in cart, will be started once user navigates away from POS.</li>\r\n\t</ul>\r\n\t</li>\r\n\t<li>Handling Canceled Orders\r\n\t<ul type=\"circle\">\r\n\t\t<li>If a user cancels an order, it will not be available for retrieval.</li>\r\n\t\t<li>Users must add items to the cart again to proceed with a new order.</li>\r\n\t</ul>\r\n\t</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><a name=\"enablement\" id=\"enablement\"></a>Enablement</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>See POS Cart Configuration guide <a href=\"https://omni.helpdocsonline.com/poscartccnfiguration-2-2$retain-cart-allowed-duration\">Retain Cart time</a>r section.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><a name=\"use-cases\" id=\"use-cases\"></a>Use Cases</h3>\r\n\r\n<table data-layout=\"default\" data-number-column=\"false\" data-table-width=\"760\" data-testid=\"renderer-table\" style=\"width: 692px;\">\r\n\t<colgroup>\r\n\t\t<col>\r\n\t\t<col>\r\n\t</colgroup>\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<th aria-sort=\"none\" colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 384px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"658\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Scenario</strong></p>\r\n\t\t\t</th>\r\n\t\t\t<th aria-sort=\"none\" colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 304px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"670\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Items in Retain in Cart</strong></p>\r\n\t\t\t</th>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"699\">User navigates from POS to other Inventory functions</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"756\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Yes</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">User adds item to cart, store pickup order and ship to address order</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px; text-align: center;\">Yes</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"765\">User applies partial&nbsp;payment to transaction</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"801\" style=\"text-align: center;\">No</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"809\">User navigates away from the receipt screen</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"849\" style=\"text-align: center;\">No</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">User in return mode</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px; text-align: center;\">Yes</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"857\">User in return mode when navigating away from the receipt screen</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"917\" style=\"text-align: center;\">No</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"925\">User clears the&nbsp;app</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"943\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Yes</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"952\">User performs post void</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"979\" style=\"text-align: center;\">No</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"987\">User logs out</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"1005\" style=\"text-align: center;\">No</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"1013\">User reaches timer expiration</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"1046\" style=\"text-align: center;\">No</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"1054\">User still within timer configuration</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"1095\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Yes</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"1104\">User performs offline transaction</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"1141\" style=\"text-align: center;\">No</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p>User performs large order (120&nbsp;line item limit), then navigates away from POS</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px; text-align: center;\">Yes</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">User performs exchange tender</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px; text-align: center;\">No</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;table&quot;,{&quot;displayMode&quot;:null,&quot;isNumberColumnEnabled&quot;:false,&quot;layout&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;localId&quot;:&quot;0881a29f-1be7-48a8-b039-582e5f1df646&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:760,&quot;__autoSize&quot;:false},&quot;tableRow&quot;,{},&quot;tableCell&quot;,{&quot;colspan&quot;:1,&quot;rowspan&quot;:1,&quot;colwidth&quot;:null,&quot;background&quot;:null}]\" data-prosemirror-content-type=\"node\" data-prosemirror-node-block=\"true\" data-prosemirror-node-name=\"paragraph\">Inactivity logout before retain cart timer expiration</p>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;table&quot;,{&quot;displayMode&quot;:null,&quot;isNumberColumnEnabled&quot;:false,&quot;layout&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;localId&quot;:&quot;0881a29f-1be7-48a8-b039-582e5f1df646&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:760,&quot;__autoSize&quot;:false},&quot;tableRow&quot;,{},&quot;tableCell&quot;,{&quot;colspan&quot;:1,&quot;rowspan&quot;:1,&quot;colwidth&quot;:null,&quot;background&quot;:null}]\" data-prosemirror-content-type=\"node\" data-prosemirror-node-block=\"true\" data-prosemirror-node-name=\"paragraph\">(All logouts will always wipe POS into an empty state)</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px; text-align: center;\">No</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;table&quot;,{&quot;displayMode&quot;:null,&quot;isNumberColumnEnabled&quot;:false,&quot;layout&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;localId&quot;:&quot;0881a29f-1be7-48a8-b039-582e5f1df646&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:760,&quot;__autoSize&quot;:false},&quot;tableRow&quot;,{},&quot;tableCell&quot;,{&quot;colspan&quot;:1,&quot;rowspan&quot;:1,&quot;colwidth&quot;:null,&quot;background&quot;:null}]\" data-prosemirror-content-type=\"node\" data-prosemirror-node-block=\"true\" data-prosemirror-node-name=\"paragraph\">Retain cart timer expiration after inactivity timeout</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px; text-align: center;\">No</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;table&quot;,{&quot;displayMode&quot;:null,&quot;isNumberColumnEnabled&quot;:false,&quot;layout&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;localId&quot;:&quot;0881a29f-1be7-48a8-b039-582e5f1df646&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:760,&quot;__autoSize&quot;:false},&quot;tableRow&quot;,{},&quot;tableCell&quot;,{&quot;colspan&quot;:1,&quot;rowspan&quot;:1,&quot;colwidth&quot;:null,&quot;background&quot;:null}]\" data-prosemirror-content-type=\"node\" data-prosemirror-node-block=\"true\" data-prosemirror-node-name=\"paragraph\">User performs BOPIS order</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px; text-align: center;\">No</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;table&quot;,{&quot;displayMode&quot;:null,&quot;isNumberColumnEnabled&quot;:false,&quot;layout&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;localId&quot;:&quot;0881a29f-1be7-48a8-b039-582e5f1df646&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:760,&quot;__autoSize&quot;:false},&quot;tableRow&quot;,{},&quot;tableCell&quot;,{&quot;colspan&quot;:1,&quot;rowspan&quot;:1,&quot;colwidth&quot;:null,&quot;background&quot;:null}]\" data-prosemirror-content-type=\"node\" data-prosemirror-node-block=\"true\" data-prosemirror-node-name=\"paragraph\">User performs Deep link order</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Yes</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">\r\n\t\t\t<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;table&quot;,{&quot;displayMode&quot;:null,&quot;isNumberColumnEnabled&quot;:false,&quot;layout&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;localId&quot;:&quot;0881a29f-1be7-48a8-b039-582e5f1df646&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:760,&quot;__autoSize&quot;:false},&quot;tableRow&quot;,{},&quot;tableCell&quot;,{&quot;colspan&quot;:1,&quot;rowspan&quot;:1,&quot;colwidth&quot;:null,&quot;background&quot;:null}]\" data-prosemirror-content-type=\"node\" data-prosemirror-node-block=\"true\" data-prosemirror-node-name=\"paragraph\">User performs GC activation/reload</p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px; text-align: center;\">Yes</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 370px;\">User navigates away from POS with expanded cart</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td colorname=\"\" colspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 290px; text-align: center;\">Yes, but POS reverts back to original cart view</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"warning\">We do NOT allow refreshing of deep link orders</div>\r\n\r\n\t  </div>\r\n </div>\r\n <div id=\"ui-page-fb-wrap\"></div>\r\n <div class=\"hiq-footer-wrap\">\r\n    \r\n                \r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
